@node Overview
@chapter Quick overview
@cindex Overview
@cindex Quick overview

EditPrefs provides a GUI to allow editing of prefs files which
are in the format:

Setting=Value
Switch
etc.

@node Requirements
@chapter Software and Hardware required
@cindex Software required
@cindex Hardware required

Requires OS3.0+.

Also needs MPGui.library (included).

@node Par
@chapter Shell Parameters
@cindex Parameters
@cindex Shell Parameters

The command line is:

EditPrefs @ref{DIR,DIR/K/A},@ref{SAVEDIR,SAVEDIR/K/A},@ref{FILE,FILE/K/A},@ref{HELP,HELP/K/A},@ref{DEFAULT,DEFAULT/K/A},@ref{GUI,GUI/K/A},@ref{PORTNAME,PORTNAME/K}.

@menu
